      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-accepting-a" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah, what is it about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, good to see you again.<BR>I've been wanting to discuss something with you. Is now a good time?</html>]]></talk_question>
