      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-accepting-acceptted" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Accept Quest)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Rumours in the Air$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>Venomous fangs waiting for their preys can be found everywhere.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Yeah, there are such rumours. But I'm not interested.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>The merchants who follow the goddess have always been interested in Merca, but I'm worried about the city's future.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Hmm?<FONT color=#7e12d2>(His ear twitches.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What rumours?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>You must have heard the rumours that Merca might be invaded by Edart Empire or Child Hirendel.<BR>But there's another rumour that has been spreading among the merchants.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's something I've never heard before.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I heard a merchant from the south has been going around gathering information in Merca.<BR>It is said that a filthy rich Child from the south with numerous merchants under her has her eyes on this city.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll try asking around.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>You can ask around if you don't believe me. I was wondering if I should send a report to President Vernicka about this but I guess you can help me do that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Talk to the merchants)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I know I'm mercenary, but I don't make things up.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-2-a" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I was wondering if you noticed anything strange lately…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Are you trying to see if I'm still spying!?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-2-b" mid="55" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Do you know how afraid I was, worried that President Vernicka might become suspicious of me again? I don't talk to a single stranger now. Well, there are those who approach me because of my pretty face, but there's nothing I can do about that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2007_sterope-3" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Anyway, it's true that I am being contacted by more new suppliers than before. Orders from the south have increased too. But the Empire's watch on goods and money passing through Merca has tightened. We should not let our guard down.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" mid="57" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Could it be a Child?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>Are there such rumours? It's true that more orders are coming in to the Honest Merchants group. I find it strange since this city might be invaded by a Child any time. Maybe there is a mastermind behind all this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1835_conscience_pope-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1835_conscience_pope-4" mid="58" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Thank you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Honest Merchant Pero$<BR>It could be a high ranking official of the Edart Empire or a Child General… But this city is known to be coveted by General Kyle. No one would dare to take any outright action unless that person has a lot of nerve. Anyway, thank you for the information. I'll check with the Honest Merchants if there is any other news.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-4-a" mid="59" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're really not interested?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>What? I didn't expect to get that kind of question from you. People usually don't think I'd be interested in Merca's safety or the conflict between Childs.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-4-b" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I didn't know there were so many spies around.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>It depends on the day. I'm a little interested today. The rumours are quite true. I see more customers who bring warm southern wind with them these days. They try to disguise themselves sometimes but they can't escape my sharp eyes. They usually buy the most expensive stuff so the sellers welcome them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-5" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'm not sure about that… Maybe I should ask Vernicka.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Merca is an open city, free for anyone to come. I hope that will remain unchanged in the future. Do you think it's possible?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5-a" mid="62" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So you knew about it already?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka gives a satisfied nod after hearing your report.)</FONT><BR>Merca's merchants surely know what to do to have such rumours passed around at times like this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5-b" mid="63" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Huh?? Do what??</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>No, I didn't have time to think about such things. But it is easy to find the source of rumours if you think about who gains from it. After hearing what you said, the merchants probably know what to do now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5-c" mid="64" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>……!!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>They should have learned that several Childs are coveting Merca and that they are spending huge sums of their own money on the city, keeping Merca's market strong. Who do you think would benefit the most from such information?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-5-d" mid="65" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Receive Reward)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Completed$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>April is a smart girl to have used you to make the rumours more trustworthy. I would need to keep my eyes wide open to lead these cunning merchants.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
